{"tid":246382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六合彩攪出13579　馬會倒貼$3150萬","createTime":"2017-05-17T03:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T15:59:48.000Z","uid":20933,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd746a0828a906e46ecb5774320e86991848c8a9","tid":246382,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:17:13.000Z","msg":"六合彩攪珠昨晚(16日)罕有「開細」，令馬會蝕本逾3000萬港元。今晚六合彩攪珠結果為1、5、7、9、10、15，特別號碼3，其中出現5個最細單數(1、3、5、7、9)，結果造就大量中獎幸運兒，頭獎有4注中，每10港元一注派彩200萬港元，而二獎及三獎分別有多達104.7注及474.7注中，每10港元一注獲馬會最低保證派彩，即分別派38,400港元及19,200港元。 <br />\n<br />\n至於第四獎至第七奬(安慰)的中獎注數，則由2千餘至逾10萬注不等。根據馬會公布，馬會在今期六合彩需補貼3150萬港元，款額從六合彩多寶儲備撥出，金額分布是頭、二、三獎合共680萬港元，第四至第七獎則達2470萬港元。"},{"pid":"d8adc215faeff566905318ca43f7c36202570311","tid":246382,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:17:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170516/mobile/bkn-20170516235536004-0516_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170516%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170516235536004-0516_00822_001.html&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=c1d64ca2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170516/mobile/bkn-20170516235536004-0516_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ff8f24fd64a45f4b74859f0e07e84d26d029a54e","tid":246382,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:18:22.000Z","msg":"平時金多寶一億一億咁賺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cadc12f8323830e11b1ae284a1b4a07d8c2dbec2","tid":246382,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:19:25.000Z","msg":"買13579果d係咪痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7a2ad3f729d31a96314a5d43405e311fd93589","tid":246382,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:19:51.000Z","msg":"散紙嚟啫"},{"pid":"6e0042942fa1957f85626e7df507773309558ff9","tid":246382,"uid